    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258628</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここは？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's this place? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はっ、そったらことも知らねーだが？
ここはお店で旅に役立つもんが
いろいろ揃ってるだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hah, you really don't know anything, do you?
This is a store where you can buy a variety
of wares. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259260</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へん！
タンス野郎が偉そうに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heh! This dresser bastard sure likes to run his tongue! </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review: Maybe something less offensive.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>たたたた、た、たんすぅ〜〜!?
ざけっでねーよ！
おらをバカにすっかもう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>D-d-d-d-dresser? What kind of showcase
of stupidity is this! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;。
アルベルトさんでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, his name is Mister Albert. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おーおーほほ、さすがは&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;だ。
おらのことをよーぐわがっでる。
優しい娘っ子だなや〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ohohoho! You're amazing &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;! You certainly 
understand me! What a nice girl! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260748</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-what? "&lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;."..? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;のために、
ここはおらが買い物の仕方、
手取り足取り教えてやるだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;'s sake, I will explain the ways
of shopping. I'll hold your hand or, if I need to do
to, your leg. So, let the teaching begin! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えーまんず、店の人間に
ちゃんと挨拶するだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>First we'll start by greeting the vendor. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おい、おめんとこ商品
買いに来てやったど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hello! We're here to buy some wares! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わ、
クローゼットが
しゃべった！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the!? A talking closet!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いや……クローゼットでも
お客様……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No... even if it's a closet it's still a customer...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いらっしゃいませ〜♪
道具屋『天地無用』へ
ようこそ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Welcome to "This side up" item store! Nice to meet you! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お探しの品は何でしょうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What items are you looking for? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263380</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ええが？
このショップ画面に入ったら、
買いたい商品を選んで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right. Once you are in the store. Select the item you want to buy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263672</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>方向キーの左右で欲しい個数を
決めるだよ。んで、&lt;icon:40&gt;1)で
買ってやればいいだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263672</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>複数の商品が欲しい場合は
まとめて買うことも
できるっちゅー話だど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you want more than one item, you can buy them all at once.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263964</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あー、商品買う前には、
ガルドが足りてるかどうか
きーっちり確認しとくだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Uh, before you buy any items, make sure you have enough Gald.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266492</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_020</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何してんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What're you doing?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_021</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今、買ったモノを
書いてるの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, I'm writing down everything we bought.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_022</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>買ったもの全部
そこに書くつもりか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Everything we bought, you're going to write it all down there?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>267184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_023</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そ。いつ、どこで、誰と、
何したか、こうして
書いとけば思いだせるでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>True but still... from now on let's remember every place 
and person so we don't run into this problem again. </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>267436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_024</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふーん……
めんどくせーこと
してんのな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh... That sounds like a pain... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>267960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_026</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>メニューのライブラリを開けば、
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;が書いたメモが
いつでも見られるだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In the Library menu you can always check the Memos that 
&lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; writes down. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>267960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_027</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これからの旅に
色々と役立つ情報ばかりだで、
こまめに確認するといいべよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's a good idea to record everything you can from now on. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268200</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_020_020_030</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さ、行こうぜ。
困った人探しの続き</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now that that's settled, let's go help some people! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
